Beyond derivations of R0 and Reff as combinations of model parameters in order to identify threshold criteria, various methods were also developed for estimating the value of R0 and its related variants from data. One of the simplest methods, valid for SIR models and closed populations, connects R0 to the final epidemic size: \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
